                     <interp inst="t17870110-56-person599" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            , the constable, apprehended the prisoners.</p>
               <p>PRISONER PRICE'S DEFENCE.</p>
               <p>I leave it to my counsel.</p>
               <p>Prisoners Rich and Bustock. We know nothing of it; we acknowledge being found in the other house.</p>
               <p>The prisoner Rich called four witnesses to his character.</p>
